name: Plastic Clothes | 半透塑料质感服饰
description:
这是一款可以添加服装为半透明塑料雨衣材质的lora模型

使用建议：

建议lora权重设置为0.4-0.9

我的常用CFG数值设置是6-8

建议搭配Ghostmix模型来使用

关键词条：Plastic raincoat，Translucent material，Functional sense，see-through

This is a lora model where you can add clothing as translucent plastic raincoat material

Suggestions for use:

It is recommended that the lora weight be set to 0.4-0.9

My usual CFG setting is 6-8

It is recommended to use with the Ghostmix model

Trigger words： Plastic raincoat，Translucent material，Functional sense，see-through
